title: Roy Haynes and Sonny Rollins Remember Morpheus
fulltitle: Roy Haynes and Sonny Rollins Remember Morpheus
description: At the rehearsal for the 50th Anniversary Carnegie Hall concert, Roy Haynes and Sonny Rollins remember one of their first recordings, "Morpheus," which is included in the box set "A Life in Time - The Roy Haynes Story" on Dreyfus Records.  For more, please visit http://www.dreyfusrecords.com
